-----------------------------------------Grid System--------------------------------------------------

→ Extra smal device (mobile phone) Bootstrap-Class: .col-xs-“number of coloms“
→ Smal device (tablets) Bootstrap-Class: .col-xs-“number of coloms“
→ Medium device Bootstrap-Class: .col-xs-“number of coloms“
→ Large device Bootstrap-Class: .col-xs-“number of coloms“


